commit.message: Add comment re primary design goal.
Add unit test to ensure that fix for #35 works.
Add workaround for issue dealing with n-dim arrays on MacOS (#35).
Travis doesn't currently support Python tests on MacOS. Sigh.
Use Xenial on Travis to test with Py3.7.
Specify how to run tests in Travis config.
Fix #31 and #32, check Py version before defining encode/tostr funcs.
Add upload command to Makefile, erase contents of dist/ when running make clean.
Import directly from msgpack rather than from private _packer, _unpacker modules; fix third party unit test.
